TEXT.S: = Rulakes = Gaga mniq Taytung Cinfungsyang ka alang Rulakes. 124 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 374 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 94% niqan 352 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 6% niqan 22 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Paiwan72%, Rukai12%, Amis2%, Bunun1%, Puyuma1%, ni rahuq na o1%.
